in heap 
********************************************************
1.for 0 based indexing 
heapify algo loop will be

        for(int i=size/2-1;i>=0;i--){
            heapify(ans,i,size);
        }
        
pos of left child  =2*i+1
pos of right child =2*i+2

********************************************************

2.for 1 based indexing 
heapify algo loop will be

        for(int i=size/2;i>0;i--){
            heapify(ans,i,size);
        }

pos of left child =2*i
pos of right child =2*i+1


